                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17851019-24-off112 t17851019-24-cd113"></join> last, two cloth coats, value 6 s. one cloth surtout coat, value 4 s. one pair of breeches, value 10 d. one pair of nankeen ditto, value 12 d. one pair of leather shoes, value 12 d. one other leather shoe, value 3 d. a leather pocket book, value 12 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
